===Ise-class Kai Ni Multi-Angle Attacks===
[[File:Air Sea Multi-Angle Attack.png|thumb|Air/Sea Multi-Angle Attack Animation|300px]]
[[File:Zuiun Multi-Angle Attack.png|thumb|Zuiun Multi-Angle Attack Animation|300px]]
*Upon remodeling to Kai Ni, {{ShipLink|Ise Kai Ni|text=Ise}} and {{ShipLink|Hyuuga Kai Ni|text=Hyuuga}} become capable of performing two different cut-ins during battle: the '''Air/Sea Multi-Angle Attack''' (海空立体攻撃) and the '''Zuiun Multi-Angle Attack''' (瑞雲立体攻撃).
*The Air/Sea Multi-Angle Attack has a '''130%''' postcap damage multiplier, whereas the Zuiun Multi-Angle Attack has a '''135%''' postcap damage multiplier.
*To trigger either of these attacks, the following initial conditions must be fulfilled:
**Air Superiority (AS) or Air Supremacy (AS+) must have been acquired during the aerial phase.
**Ise/Hyuuga must not be heavily damaged (at or below 25% HP) (大破).
**At least one [[List of Main Guns by stats|main gun]] must be equipped on Ise/Hyuuga.
*From there, the possible cut-ins that can be triggered depend on the planes that Ise/Hyuuga have equipped.
**To trigger the Air/Sea Multi-Angle Attack, at least two dive bombers must be equipped. Possible dive bombers that can be used to meet this requirement are as follows:<table><td>{{EquipmentLink|Suisei Model 22 (634 Air Group)|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Suisei Model 22 (634 Air Group/Skilled)|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Suisei Model 12 (634 Air Group w/ Type 3 Cluster Bombs)|icon=true}}</td></table>
**To trigger the Zuiun Multi-Angle Attack, at least two Zuiuns must be equipped. Possible Zuiuns that can be used to meet this requirement are as follows:<table><td>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun (634 Air Group)|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun Model 12|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun Model 12 (634 Air Group)|icon=true}}</td><td>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun (631 Air Group)|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun (634 Air Group/Skilled)|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun Kai Ni (634 Air Group)|icon=true}}<br>{{EquipmentLink|Zuiun Kai Ni (634 Air Group/Skilled)|icon=true}}</td></table>